@layer -1 (last transformer block, pre-lm_head)
@personas school_idol senpai knight sorceress noir_detective horror_whisper childhood_friend demon_lord childlike stoic_mentor
@scale 10 (expansion to 20 tracked in roadmap_dest_consciousness.json P1.next)
@seeds_per_persona 7 Korean text samples (inline in pod payload, NOT committed)
@neutral_n 12 generic Korean factual/descriptive baseline
@normalization L2 unit norm per steering vector
@alpha_default 60.0 (v2 continuation prompts — tuned vs 6/20/40/60/80/120/200 sweep)
@alpha_sweep_summary a=6:shift=0.22 min=0.0  a=60:shift=0.917 min=0.797  a=120:shift=0.952 min=0.878  a=200:shift=0.953 min=0.903 (quality degrades)

