@weight_emergent_proof persona_vectors.npz 10 × 5120 in hidden-state manifold, applied via layer[-1] pre-lm_head forward hook (persona_apply.pypayload PersonaRuntime._hook). Zero system_prompt, zero persona-token, zero user-side template in inference code path (verified: enc = tokenizer(prompt, ...) where prompt = bare user text). File: /workspace/p1/persona_apply.pypayload (pod-only, emitted by serving/persona_apply.hexa)

